
<h1 class="title underline--magical grey-text text-lighten-3">Create your BDGT</h1>
<li class="bdgt-listing">
  <span>Input your monthly income</span>
</li>
<li class="bdgt-listing">
  <span>Input your planned purchase</span>
</li>
<li class="bdgt-listing spacing">
  <span>Generate your suggested budget to afford your purchase!</span>
</li>
